#: src/LegalNoticeSupport.php:231
msgid ""
"The use of the contact data published by us as part of the imprint "
"obligation by third parties for the purpose of sending unsolicited "
"advertising and information material is hereby expressly prohibited. We "
"expressly reserve the right to take legal action in the event of unsolicited "
